Next year’s debt should range from 900 billion to a trillion kronor,” said David Marek, an analyst at Patria Finance, to the server iHNed.cz.
Similarly, Vladimír Pikora, analyst at Next Finance, says: “We could come to exceed a trillion in 2009.
